oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Martha White Flour Job No. 37748
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: Accounting; Hatch Show Print (Firm); Jim and Jesse; Martha White Foods;
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Invoice (No. 2296) for an order placed by Martha White Flour for 50 two color window cards for a performance by Jim and Jesse at the School Auditorium in Elleville, Georgia, on January 15. Poster indicates the agreed price, quantity, shipping method, and a description of the posters.
